Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.11,0:03:09.30,Main,,0,0,0,,{They sure are disrespectful fellows.}Những anh bạn bất lịch sự.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.32,0:03:13.27,Main,,0,0,0,,{The escape route!}Đến lối thoát hiểm!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.42,0:03:15.42,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Hey?}Sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.17,0:03:17.05,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Hey, hey!}Này!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.76,0:03:21.38,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Idiot!}Đồ ngu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.38,0:03:22.01,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Shit!}Chết tiệt!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.30,0:03:25.76,Main,,0,0,0,,{Hey, hey, hey!}Này!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.78,0:03:37.02,Main,,0,0,0,,{Escape route! [9 frames]}Đó là lối thoát của ta!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.16,0:03:47.33,Main,,0,0,0,,{Chi of Earth!}Khí của đất!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.52,0:04:06.97,Main,,0,0,0,,{That was really close! [9 frames]}Suýt thì tiêu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.44,0:04:11.23,Main,,0,0,0,,{I'm glad you're safe.}Cháu mừng là chú an toàn.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.44,0:04:27.67,Main,split,0,0,0,,{What are you doing?}Mấy người làm gì đó?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.67,0:04:29.83,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Hey, over there... Who is that?}Này. Đó là ai vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.53,0:04:35.58,Main,,0,0,0,,{I wonder if she's a new girlfriend.}Có lẽ là bạn gái mới?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.58,0:04:37.30,Main,,0,0,0,,{For that, she's rather young.}Quá trẻ để làm bạn gái.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.30,0:04:39.52,Main,,0,0,0,,{Weird one, hot dog bun, loved one!}Buổi chiều, thả diều, bên người yêu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.52,0:04:41.26,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Maybe she's his secret love-child?}Hay là cô con gái từ mối tình bí mật?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.26,0:04:42.81,Main,split,0,0,0,,{For that, she's rather old.}Quá già để là con gái.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.81,0:04:45.22,Main,,0,0,0,,{Child, mild, wild!}Bòn bon, quả bồ hòn, đứa trẻ con.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.31,0:04:49.35,Main,,0,0,0,,{But I'm surprised.}Nhưng chú ngạc nhiên đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.35,0:04:53.19,Main,,0,0,0,,{I wasn't expecting Pao's daughter\Nto be this old already...}Khi thấy con gái của Pao đã lớn thế này.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.70,0:04:56.04,Main,,0,0,0,,{You probably don't remember,}Có thể cháu không nhớ,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.04,0:04:59.02,Main,,0,0,0,,{but I met you once when\Nyou were this little.}nhưng chú đã gặp cháu một lần,\Nkhi cháu còn nhỏ thế này.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.72,0:05:03.24,Main,,0,0,0,,{How do you know my father?}Chú biết bố cháu như thế nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.24,0:05:05.73,Main,,0,0,0,,{How?}Như thế nào ư?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.73,0:05:08.93,Main,,0,0,0,,{Just an acquaintance.\NIt's been 10 years already.}Ông ấy là người quen của chú.\NCũng đã mười năm rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.46,0:05:13.66,Main,,0,0,0,,{But your father sure was unlucky\Nto be in a traffic accident...}Tai nạn giao thông của bố cháu\Nthật là quá xui xẻo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.16,0:05:20.04,Main,combine,0,0,0,,{On the way to Jupiter, there was a sudden\Nspatial fluctuation in hyperspace...}Trên đường đến Sao Mộc,\Ncó một biến động đột ngột trong không gian.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.04,0:05:24.10,Main,,0,0,0,,{Here you go.}Em mời chị.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.70,0:05:25.60,Main,,0,0,0,,{Thank you.}Cảm ơn em.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.92,0:05:30.05,Main,,0,0,0,,{Are you the "girlfriend?"}Chị là bồ anh ấy à?
