Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.82,0:05:43.23,Main,,0,0,0,,{Rejected!}Bị từ chối!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.29,0:05:49.20,Main,,0,0,0,,{Mr. Jet, why were you at the graveyard?}Chú Jet, sao chú lại ở nghĩa trang?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.18,0:05:53.35,Main,,0,0,0,,{Nobody outside the family knows\Nhe got into an accident...}Không ai ngoài gia đình cháu\Nbiết bố cháu gặp tai nạn.
