Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.20,0:06:51.86,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Of course not...}Tất nhiên rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.86,0:06:53.10,Main,,0,0,0,,{Let's go!}Đi thôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.89,0:06:58.95,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{to repay to Pao or this girl,}{\i0}{\i1}Không phải là vì tôi nợ Pao hay cô bé này,{\i0}
